steps.name: When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"

When I delete molecule with name JIT006Molecule and verify
When I delete molecule with name duplicatedJIT006Molecule and verify
When I add new molecule with name JIT006Molecule
When I add new molecule with name duplicatedJIT006Molecule
Then I should see the molecule with name JIT006Molecule display in list Components
Then I should see the molecule with name duplicatedJIT006Molecule display in list Components
When I rename molecule name from JIT006Molecule to invalid_updateJIT006Molecule
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Special characters are not allowed"
When I close the modal popup
When I rename molecule name from JIT006Molecule to empty
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Name is required"
When I close the modal popup
When I rename molecule name from JIT006Molecule to duplicatedJIT006Molecule
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Name has been taken, Please use another one"
When I close the modal popup
When I rename molecule name from JIT006Molecule to updateJIT006Molecule
Then I should see slider message with content "Updated molecule successfully"
Then I should see the molecule with name updateJIT006Molecule display in list Components
